#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:1
msgid "RedshiftExtrapolator 使用与原理说明"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:3
msgid ""
"本文档详细解释 `autohea.core.utils.RedshiftExtrapolator` "
"的物理推导、计算流程与使用方法，重点阐述“在给定信噪比阈值下可探测的最大红移”的计算原理。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:5
msgid "源码位置：`autohea/src/autohea/core/utils.py`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:6
msgid "相关函数：`compute()`、`find_redshift_for_snr()`、`snr_li_ma()`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:10
msgid "1. 问题背景与目标"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:12
msgid "目标：在给定的XSPEC物理模型、仪器响应（ARF/RMF）、背景与曝光时间条件下，求在某个SNR阈值（如 7σ）时的最大可探测红移 z_max。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:14
msgid "核心变量："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:15
msgid "模型 M(E; params)：XSPEC光子数谱（photons cm⁻² keV⁻¹ s⁻¹）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:16
msgid "仪器响应：ARF（有效面积）与 RMF（能量重分配）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:17
msgid "背景计数与时长：`bkgnum`, `duration`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:18
msgid "SNR阈值：`snr_target`（默认7）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:22
msgid "2. 物理论证与关键公式"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:24
msgid "记观测到的光子数谱为 N_obs(E_obs)。类中遵循以下“严格的XSPEC红移外推公式”："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:26
msgid "几何衰减（真实物理距离）：使用共动距离 r_c(z)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:28
msgid "光子数密度按真实距离平方反比衰减：∝ 1/r_c²"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:29
msgid "因此归一化的几何因子："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:31
msgid "r_c 因子 = [r_c(z₀) / r_c(z)]²"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:33
msgid "K-correction（幂律谱示例）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:35
msgid "若 N_rest(E) ∝ E^(-α)，则红移导致能量变换 E_rest = E_obs × (1+z)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:36
msgid "XSPEC的单位与红移下时间膨胀、能量间隔效应相互抵消，最终只需要能谱幂律的额外修正："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:38
msgid "K 因子 = ((1+z₀) / (1+z))^α"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:40
msgid "归一化缩放总因子"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:42
msgid "设 `norm_original` 为 z₀ 时模型的归一化，z 时应使用："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:44
msgid "norm_new = norm_original × ((1+z₀)/(1+z))^α × [r_c²(z₀)/r_c²(z)]"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:46
msgid "这正是代码中 `find_redshift_for_snr()` 计算 `total_factor` 的来源："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:48
msgid "`geometric_factor = (r_c_z0 / r_c_grid) ** 2`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:49
msgid "`k_correction_factor = ((1 + z0) / (1 + z_grid)) ** alpha`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:50
msgid "`total_factor = k_correction_factor * geometric_factor`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:52
msgid ""
"注：光度距离 D_L = (1+z) r_c 是定义量，适合用于能量通量 F 与光度 L "
"的关系；但对光子数密度与XSPEC模型的处理，采用真实距离 r_c 更能直接体现几何衰减，因此本类选择 r_c。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:56
msgid "3. 计算流程（逐步说明）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:58
msgid "以 `compute(snr_target=7)` → `find_redshift_for_snr()` 的实际实现为主线："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:60
msgid "3.1 模型初始化与参数注入"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:62
msgid "`init_model()` 内部依次执行："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:63
msgid "初始化HEASoft环境，创建 `xspec.Model(self._model)` 实例；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:64
msgid "`_set_par()` 将传入的 `par` 按模型参数顺序写入XSPEC，并冻结参数；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:65
msgid "自动识别红移参数（若存在 `...Redshift`）与归一化参数（通常为最后一组件的 `norm`）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:67
msgid "3.2 红移网格与缩放因子"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:69
msgid "初始红移区间 [zmin, zmax]（默认 [z0, z0+1]），生成均匀 `z_grid`；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:70
msgid "依次计算："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:71
msgid "`r_c_z0 = comoving_distance(z0)`；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:72
msgid "`r_c_grid = comoving_distance(z_grid)`；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:73
msgid "`geometric_factor = (r_c_z0 / r_c_grid) ** 2`；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:74
msgid "`alpha = _get_spectral_index()` 自动识别幂指数；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:75
msgid "`k_correction_factor = ((1 + z0) / (1 + z_grid)) ** alpha`；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:76
msgid "`total_factor = k_correction_factor * geometric_factor`。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:78
msgid "随后对每个 z："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:79
msgid "如果模型含有红移参数：`self._par_z.values = z`；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:80
msgid "始终按公式修正归一化：`self._par_norm.values = original_norm * total_factor[i]`。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:82
msgid "3.3 谱→计数率（卷积）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:84
msgid "使用 SOXS 完成谱与响应的卷积："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:85
msgid "`spec = soxs.Spectrum.from_pyxspec_model(self._m1)`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:86
msgid "取能段 0.5–4.0 keV：`newspec = spec.new_spec_from_band(0.5, 4.0)`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:87
msgid "指定响应与曝光：设置 `rmf`, `arf`, `bkg`, `exposure`, `backExposure`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:88
msgid "用 ARF 卷积得到计数谱：`cspec = newspec * soxs.AuxiliaryResponseFile(arf)`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:89
msgid "总计数率：`src_rate = cspec.rate.sum().value`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:90
msgid "叠加背景贡献（按您的数据口径）：`total_rate = src_rate + (bkgnum/duration) * area_ratio`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:92
msgid "最终计数：`total_counts = total_rate * duration`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:94
msgid "3.4 SNR 计算（Li & Ma公式）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:96
msgid "使用 `snr_li_ma(n_src, n_bkg, alpha_area_time)`："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:98
msgid "`n_src = total_counts`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:99
msgid "`n_bkg = bkgnum`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:100
msgid "`alpha_area_time = area_ratio`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:102
msgid "返回："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:104
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"SNR = sqrt{ 2 [ N_on ln((1+α)/α × N_on/(N_on+N_off)) + N_off ln((1+α) × "
"N_off/(N_on+N_off)) ] }"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:106
msgid "该公式对高能天文的 on/off 计数统计更稳健。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:108
msgid "3.5 自适应搜索 z_max"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:110
msgid "在 `z_grid` 上找到 SNR 首次低于 `snr_target` 的位置 [z1, z2]；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:111
msgid "在 [z1, z2] 区间递归细分，线性插值求解 SNR(z)=目标阈值；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:112
msgid "若整个区间 SNR 都高于阈值，逐步扩大上界（`max_expand` 次）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:116
msgid "4. 推导要点回顾（为何这样做）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:118
msgid "使用共动距离 r_c："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:119
msgid "光子数密度是与真实几何距离相关的量，选 r_c 体现 1/r² 衰减；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:120
msgid "时间膨胀与能量间隔效应在 XSPEC 光子数谱单位下相互抵消。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:122
msgid "K-correction 的来源："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:123
msgid "对幂律谱 N ∝ E^-α，能量红移带来额外的 (1+z)^-α 因子；"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:124
msgid "最终只需考虑该能谱倾斜产生的修正。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:126
msgid "统一修正归一化："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:127
msgid "无论是否存在 \".Redshift\" 参数，归一化都乘以总因子 `total_factor`，保证谱形在观测能段内的正确缩放。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:131
msgid "5. 使用示例"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:155
msgid "6. 常见问题与注意事项"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:157
msgid "XSPEC 与 HEASoft：需正确初始化 HEASoft 环境（类内部已调用 `HeasoftEnvManager`）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:158
msgid "SOXS 版本差异：部分属性在不同版本可能只读，但不影响卷积计算。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:159
msgid "模型参数顺序：`par` 必须与 XSPEC 模型参数顺序完全一致。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:160
msgid "红移参数缺失：若模型不含显式红移参数，依旧按 `total_factor` 修正归一化。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:161
msgid "能段选择：示例固定为 0.5–4.0 keV，如需更改可拓展接口。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:162
msgid "背景口径：`total_rate` 中背景项与 `area_ratio` 的口径请与数据处理保持一致。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:166
msgid "7. 验证方法"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:168
msgid "使用 `verify_redshift_extrapolation(z_test)` 可输出详细的几何因子、K 因子与总因子，帮助核对推导："
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:174
msgid "打印 r_c、K-correction、总因子与文本解释，便于交叉验证。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../RedshiftExtrapolator.md:178
msgid "8. 后续改进建议"
msgstr ""

